I did this for a mega collab with my friends, the collab itself is not done, but my part is:

Deku is adorable no matter who draws him honestly.

blog.description: I'll do "correct" quotes because we all know they said this shit I'm writing!!!( Match ups and s/o | what if bnha scenarios huns)

body:
let’s talk about bakugos mom

alright I’ve Seen so many hate posts and Start asking myself if people slowly lose track of reality?

I mean, if it would be a realistic show everyone would be in friking jail guys.

but it’s an anime, a manga - not real

mitsuki is shown to be tsundere like mean and violent in the outside but kind on the Inside. she is meant to be a funny character by scolding her son - a little bit like sakura always slapping naruto. you can even see it by looking at their Animation and mimic, showing ja Comic like emotions.

abusive in the real World but in this show teacher punch students in the stomache so hard they vomit so everyone is kind of abusive in there.

ITS FICTIONAL. NOT REAL. PLEASE CONCENTRATE ON REAL PROBLEMS

summary: HOLY SHIT THIS TOOK MAYBE A TOTAL OF 5 HOURS AND I ACTUALLY LIKE IT???????? I’m so proud of this cuz I’ve never drawn actual...
caption:
HOLY SHIT THIS TOOK MAYBE A TOTAL OF 5 HOURS AND I ACTUALLY LIKE IT????????

I’m so proud of this cuz I’ve never drawn actual explosions before. I’ve also never done a pose like this before.

And if you want a blood-free version…

BOOM BITCH. I THOUGHT OF THAT TOO.

This is also the first time I’ve used a set color palette. It’s called Just Enough of Forever and I found it on @color-palettes. They’ve got some really good, user-submitted palettes on there. I’ve saved like 20 of them.

blog.name: theenigmaofriversong
blog.title: The Long way round
blog.description: Clara sometimes asks me if I dream. Of course I dream, I tell her. Everybody dreams. But what do you dream about, she'll ask. The same thing everybody dreams about, I tell her. I dream about where I'm going. She always laughs at that. But you're not going anywhere, you're just wandering about. That's not true. Not any more. I have a new destination. My journey is the same as yours, the same as anyones. It's taken me so many years, so many lifetimes, but at last I know where I'm going. Where I've always been going. Home...

summary: if the Geneva Conventions are still a thing in the bnha universe, which i doubt, then nedzu is a war criminal. if im wrong tell...
body: if the Geneva Conventions are still a thing in the bnha universe, which i doubt, then nedzu is a war criminal. if im wrong tell me, but having child soldiers is a war crime. provisional heroes are still minors, and even if theyre not in ‘war’ thats semantics, they still see active combat with a choice of death. idk id like to see more discussion abt the ramifications of things like this, of the world sinking backward as the government weaponizes children
